LOCUS       tRNA-gRNA_position_[M1_n-1]_(GB1210) 3222 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  tRNA and scaffold for the assembly of GBoligomers for the first
            position (positon [M1_n-1]) of a polycistronic tRNA-gRNA regulated
            by the (monocot) U3 promoter (2-part multiplexing).
